 \varphi(a^i a^j) = \varphi(a^{i+j}) = b^{(i+j)k} = b^{ik} b^{jk} = \varphi(a^i) \varphi(a^j) 
 a^i = a^j \implies \varphi(a^i) = \varphi(a^j)  
